eschcholtzia
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:[<i>E. californica</i> as a profuse and beautiful introduced weed of southern NZ riverbeds, remarkable for the difficulty of its spelling.] =Californian poppy,.
Origin:[none]
